works.title: Associations between symptoms of eating disturbance and frequency of physical activity in a non-clinical, population-based sample of adolescents
works.abstract:
Background
Physical activity is an important factor related to eating disorders, but the relationship between symptoms of eating disorders and physical activity is multifaceted.
